    "PheKnowLator is open-source and available through GitHub (https://github.com/callahantiff/PheKnowLator) and PyPI (https://pypi.org/project/pkt-kg).",
    "Important manuscript definitions are provided in Supplementary Table 1, acronyms are provided in Supplementary Table 2, and PheKnowLator ecosystem resources are listed in Supplementary Tables 3 and 4.",
